{"tid":924161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"22歲情困男墮樓 送院不治","createTime":"2018-12-02T01:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T03:22:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1afa6afc3f7737d04a801177959be7ef6c2edc1c","tid":924161,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T01:01:20.000Z","msg":"石硤尾澤安邨麗澤樓，凌晨近2時，一名姓梁22歲男子從高處墮下，倒臥地上昏迷。救護員接報到場，將事主送院搶救，惜終於不治。<br />\n據稱，事主從事藍領工作，與伯父及父親同住上址。他曾有一位同居女友，惟兩個月前分手，自此顯得鬱鬱不歡。事發時他與伯父在家，伯父正在睡覺。警方現場撿獲遺書，調查沒有可疑。<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181202/large/1543694038_bbfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181202%2Flarge%2F1543694038_bbfb.jpg&h=e99e8f1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181202/58982076\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181202%2F58982076&d=mFcDTmB5Gv4gX2rcP0LKDL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=247a7f82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181202%2F58982076&h=f4460618\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181202/58982076</a>"},{"pid":"6cf2d15e047796974b9a51b9b66c4d042216c516","tid":924161,"uid":10692,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T01:04:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5943a1f0c81b975582c518a21d3cb993ed2d8122","tid":924161,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T01:05:27.000Z","msg":"公屋1分"},{"pid":"893993e1f5b3d22868564dc8d29a1bc2a94e9c32","tid":924161,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"re